# ── Privacy belt-and-braces ─────────────────────────────────────────
# User data lives OUTSIDE this repo (~/Documents/Agenda), so it can never
# be committed. These rules are extra safety nets in case an encrypted
# blob or a data folder ever ends up in the project tree by mistake.
*.dat
dati/
backups/

# ── Build output ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
build/
Agenda.app/
*.iconset

# ── Python / macOS / tooling cruft ──────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.DS_Store
.claude/
.playwright-mcp/
